summary:
- **Stop Loss Trigger Event**: Two CitiFirst MINIs (XJOKOY and LOVKOT) have been suspended due to hitting their Stop Loss Levels.  
  - **XJOKOY**: Underlying (S&P ASX 200 Futures Sep-2025) traded at/below Stop Loss Level of 8622.0000.  
  - **LOVKOT**: Underlying (LOVISA HOLDINGS LTD) traded at/above Stop Loss Level of 33.9200.  
- **Trading & Settlement**:  
  - Temporary trading resumption from 2pm next trading day until 4pm the following day.  
  - Holders can sell to Citigroup at the Stop Loss Amount during this window.  
  - If unsold, automatic termination with payment within 10 business days.  

*No other material information identified.*
